# Track:
#   CLAUDE.md
#   paper_notes/             ← Harry's reading annotations (L1)
#   daily/                   ← auto-captured conversation traces (L3)
#   knowledge/               ← LLM-compiled concept articles (L4)
#   docs/research_*.md       ← Harry's synthesis (L2)
#   experiments/*/           ← experiment code & READMEs

# Paper PDFs — large binary, fetched from arxiv, not in git
paper_notes/pdfs/

